title: Client Wont Launch
body: I'm running into issues, I run the launcher as admin, it comes up with the LAUNCH button, but what ever I try I can't get it to launch into the login screen. Tried disabling Anti-Virus and everything and still nothing. Reinstalled already and nothing.

replies.body: Which OS are you on and who's your ISP?

Im getting a similar issue after the latest patch, It comes up with the launch button but when I click it it plays the sound effect and does nothing, even after following riots troubleshooting guides...
